<i>adverb</i>: 설레설레 [설레설레] <i>noun</i>: 요동 [요동] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>설레설레 [설레설레]</dt><br>
<dd>shaking; waving; wagging</dd><br>
<dd>머리, 고개, 꼬리 등 몸의 일부분을 가볍게 자꾸 좌우로 흔드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of a person or animal shaking a part of his/her or its head, tail, etc., from side to side.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>요동 [요동]</dt><br>
<dd>shaking; rocking; jolting</dd><br>
<dd>흔들려 움직임. 또는 흔들어 움직임.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of shaking something to move it, or a state in which something shakes and moves.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>